Package com.streetsofboston.smugmug.v1_2_1.system

Interface Summary
IEnumValue<T> Helper interface for translating enumerated variables into instances of type T.
IHasID Every Smugmug Object has an ID.
ISmugObject<T> This interface defines all the methods that can be invoked publicly on every type of Smugmug Object.
ISmugObjectPrototype<T extends ISmugObject<T>> Prototypes are objects that hold data from which real instances can be created.
 

Class Summary
Account This class represents a User account on Smugmug.
Session This class represents a logged-in Session.
SmugAttribute<T> This class represents attributes for Smugmug objects.
Stats<T extends ISmugObject<T>> Defines the statistics for an object of type T given a year and a month.
